data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! Whether you're looking for a great starter home, second home, or investment property, this condo fits the bill. This cute 2 bedroom 1 ½ bath condo is nestled right next to Georgetown Lake in historic Georgetown CO. New LVP flooring throughout, new paint & textured walls, butcher block countertops and updated light fixtures. Large utility room with area for washer/dryer.  The living room has a cozy wood burning fireplace and opens to the attached deck for easy entertaining.  Minutes to Loveland Ski Area, and 8 other world-class ski resorts including Vail, Breckenridge and Keystone.  All are super-close.! Day trips include Mt Blue Sky, St Mary's Glacier, Rocky Mountain National Park, Guanella Pass and much more! Walk out your front door and visit the local brewery, restaurants & shops in town.  Go fishing or kayaking on the lake and enjoy local hiking trails, or Clear Creek is mere steps out the back, for an easy fishing or kayaking excursion.   Short-term rentals are allowed by the HOA but please check with the city of Georgetown for additional restrictions and guidelines. Call City Hall for more information (303) 569-2555.  Take a look at everything Georgetown https://www.townofgeorgetown.us/ Seller will offer a one-year home warranty through American Home Shield.
